Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时空的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙里有一群黄金族
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们创造星群
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有预知能力的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.46,0:00:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤那些还没成熟的其他种族
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回应了这个呼唤的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.35,0:00:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白银族
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青铜族
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄族
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来英雄族引发了战争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量的种族濒临灭绝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金族把战争平息时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.83,0:00:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄族就只剩下5个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金族要惩罚活下来的5个英雄族人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们寄宿到比自己更弱小的种族里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那些弱小的种族而生存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿了英雄族灵魂的人称为诺多斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.07,0:01:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为了掌握宇宙命运的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.52,0:01:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中具有巨大力量的英雄族贝尔库罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿到了最后冲出宇宙的最弱小的种族——黑铁族 也就是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一名叫做艾吉的少年的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超空间跳跃系统正常启动确认
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有5分钟就去到“星之道”的汇合坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来本舰要进行超空间航行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:00:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“星之道”的“占星术”确定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs18}译注：占星术（Horoscope）--"星之道"只能透过特定流动的波形来表示。而"占星术"就是包\N含航行的所有具体状况在内的综合情报。在"星之道"中进行超空间跳跃必须确定"占星术"。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航路代号L2S-527896CYY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“星标”确定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs18}译注：星标（Astral Sign）--由"星流"产生的固定波形。星流（AstralCurrent）--由天体\N间的引力形成的"流动"。这个流动与液体或气体的流动不同，具有双向性的特征。这个\N双向性在假说中与循环流向的构造有关。航线的极性决定航线上受到哪个方向的推力。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接确定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航路 L2S-527896CYY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接确立
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始试读“占星术”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部天帆 依照航路展开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离“占星术”确定还有180秒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是太阳系第三行星 我们人类的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个世纪以前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球被青铜族占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类现在连接近太阳系也办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的生存权
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断被想灭亡人类的白银族以及
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们麾下的青铜族夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们人类决心要夺回地球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而唯一的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾吉 就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你体内寄宿着英雄族的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正是……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“爸爸们”说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪安奈拉来找我的话 就随她们一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我不得不做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我可以继续在阿尔哥诺特里面参观吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鲁 美鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们带路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经理解了自己的使命了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位贵人好像已经领悟到了12条契约
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及现在在这船上的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,320){\fscy230}英  雄  族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运行“占星术” 开始设定超空间航线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常引擎关闭 全部天帆下方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dimension Ripper（时空割裂机）启动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Warp In（进入超空间）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exception（非规则）领域包裹船身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Astral Sail（星间航线）导入坐标轴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航线展开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速装置在使用范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Warp Sataus（超空间跳跃方位）巡航确认
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰在二个周期后终于平安回到“星之道”了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是因为有大家的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们的旅程还不到一半
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在把救世主送到阿尔特利亚前 绝对不能松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs18}译注：阿尔特利亚--尤诺斯王家所在的星系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预防发生遭遇战 先准备好战术程序
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅程还长着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第41到第50欧钢队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs18}译注：欧岗--人类开发的人型兵器。与过去的机器不同，不需要使用感觉\N变化程序，因此能操作到像自己的肉体那样灵活，能做出至今都不可能做\N到的高难度动作，从而也可以采用手枪等外部兵器，能够进行广域的作战。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入20分钟的待机时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第21到第30欧钢队……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护公主和公主乘坐的这条船是我们的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要依靠那样的猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舔了可能会死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是油漆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油漆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涂在墙壁或欧钢上的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涂上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在封锁货物区域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立即避难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在封锁货物区域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾吉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么回事 说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我鼓励你们积极地去与他交流
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会起到什么启蒙效果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然如此 助长他胡来的行为我可不赞同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个猴子竟然是救世主 真难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与诺多斯斗气 她们真大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女儿们给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我监督无方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以为诺多斯的存在只会引起船内恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪安奈拉公主说他已经理解了自己的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一点我也同意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他表示了为我们战斗的诚意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些骚动也只是天真的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是船员们的反应太敏感了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看来都很畏惧他的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个原始人就是救世主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们目睹到诺多斯的力量后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船员们会骚动起来也并不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那只是恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是应该教育一下他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难为你 不过就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让那个猴子安静下来的话 我们也无法安心带他回阿尔特利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要从外观开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想光是改变下他的穿着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给船员们的印象也会很不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:11:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾吉自身可能也会因为一身整洁的打扮而产生某种自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干净多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来是剪头发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我示范给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算剪了也很快会长回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像Food那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 也不会痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发剪好后 接下来就是这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在船上穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样更方便行动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 那个在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油漆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个墙壁你可以随意涂写
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为换衣服这种事 他会马上答应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是剪头发这件事就已经表明他对我们的道具感兴趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伟大的善心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是胡乱涂油漆而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是诺多斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他也有这一面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪了头发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是迪安奈拉公主的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那猴子驯服了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久之前的欧隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫芪萜 还盛开了很多别的花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Food最爱吃的东西是波斯特的树根
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是数量并不多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星欧隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望把它复原吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是诺多斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其他黑铁族了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须见识下诺多斯的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到很强的杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人正逼近这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是白银族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能捕捉到敌船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在能搜敌的范围内没反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是敌人正逼近这件事绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发出战术程序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战术程序得出的结论是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过Active Warp来回避敌人是最佳方案
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs18}译注：Active Warp--超空间跳跃的一种，与一般的超空间跳跃不同的是：\N一般的Warp要利用"星之道"，即按照"占星术"来运行，\N而Active Warp则不利用"星之道"，由己方主动（active）操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是Active Warp无法正确设定航线
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人不知道我们在哪里Warp Out（跳出超空间）的话 就无法追来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:15:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地是法隆星系和紫苑星系间延伸的广大黑暗空间的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在质量巨大的物体旁边Warp Out的可能性无限接近零
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是说没有危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以认为危险性极低 迪安奈拉公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在能量填充途中 保护层以及所有能量兵器的 使用都受到限制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防御力处在极低的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们在能量填充完成后 就离开“星之道” 进入Active Warp
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不想脱离“星之道”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不能把敌人带到故乡去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 请下判断
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我允许
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“星之道”上出现了大量物体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是青铜族的蚁冢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Warp Out（跳出超空间）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 贝尔库罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WEAPON62 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡雷普阿全部集中到前方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后方就交给诺多斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防御开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 不要拖那猴子的后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:18:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白银族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们力量相差太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入Active Warp
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全队归舰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺多斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的诺多斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量填充完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dimension Ripper（时空割裂机）启动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Astral Turbine engine（星间涡轮引擎）全开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Warp In（进入超空间）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐标确认
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎就在目标区域的正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围没有敌影以及重力震
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战结束 摆脱敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及我们的诺多斯的力量所取得的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样能稍微减轻大家对艾吉的恐惧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位贵人都会为我们而战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我们对他有什么想法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铭刻在内心的破坏与灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明知这份痛楚 却为了我们……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下居然会主动去触摸别人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五个人出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为了补给而路过行星枢纽体塔罗斯 在那 里遇到了另一名诺多斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.76,0:23:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 Heroic Age
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第4话 行星体塔罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.16,0:22:32.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}ずっと前から君のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.25,0:22:37.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}知っていたけどこんな気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:42.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}芽生えるなんて思わなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:48.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}まさか君に恋するなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.29,0:22:52.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}何気ない帰り道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:22:58.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}夜空の星を見上げながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:23:03.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}わざと遠回りして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.28,0:23:10.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}君の肩にもたれて歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.57,0:23:17.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}二人でいれば　どんなことでも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:23.02,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}乗り越えられそうと言う君の
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.10,0:23:28.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}真っすぐな瞳を見つめて思う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:34.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
